開機會辨識hardware，唔知點解換cpu/raid卡/底板都有機會出事，我見過好多次"},{"pid":"303de390bb5b1be7611fee5328ffc985ad99e1e1","tid":810262,"uid":33587,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-09-08T02:49:12.000Z","msg":"重裝咗windows未"},{"pid":"2cd1cd7e4e8b60297680d2567f9fc492b3113ed3","tid":810262,"uid":37232,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-08T02:51:03.000Z","msg":"我買重死hdd or hdd綫插唔好 (5成以上)"},{"pid":"9c917e1a5a00c329ac4f1207d70d24f499eeeab1","tid":810262,"uid":37232,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-09-08T02:51:30.000Z","msg":"其次係driver os software問題"},{"pid":"09a6993576a36ebd9710ffbffa2729e8a471ed92","tid":810262,"uid":97182,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-08T04:56:33.000Z","msg":"大多數情況下換CPU或者換底板，重新裝Windows都係指定動作"},{"pid":"51fe94a13d13e1331e6f81e974e162e025779ee2","tid":810262,"uid":48624,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-09-08T05:46:37.000Z","msg":"會唔會電壓問題？ check下兩粒CPU裝上機後 個電壓分別係幾多 test前分別都reset bios <br />\n利申：唔係電腦專家"},{"pid":"6aa976bd4802af48f8591fb4996a09726699639d","tid":810262,"uid":51711,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-09-08T05:53:40.000Z","msg":"有冇update bios?"},{"pid":"a2f611b1abe15b83e05aaf2bdfa54006f7854179","tid":810262,"uid":75694,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"04e90235e65a1c15659b8fb560120e6d49ae1b3f","tid":810262,"uid":45252,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"6d1680b4a86e52e4a2eb9341714ad0d9a6363e2d","tid":810262,"uid":120558,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-09-07T21:39:32.000Z","msg":"先睇下配置：<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\nsocket 775<br />\nCPU : E2160<br />\nMotherboard : MSI Boston MS-7525<br />\nHDD 500GB<br />\nPower : 560W （唔記得牌子 後來換上去嘅）<br />\nGraphic Card : HD 6850<br />\nOS: Windows 10<br />\n<br />\n是咁的<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n屋企有部以前家人買嘅775 socket 廠機 <br />\n呢排想upgra