\nHDD 500GB<br />\nPower : 560W （唔記得牌子 後來換上去嘅）<br />\nGraphic Card : HD 6850<br />\nOS: Windows 10<br />\n<br />\n是咁的<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n屋企有部以前家人買嘅775 socket 廠機 <br />\n呢排想upgrade 俾屋企人繼續用 叫幫部機續下命咁<br />\n換完電+Graphic 都冇事<br />\n但後來換埋粒E7600之後就一開入唔到Windows <br />\n<br />\n大概情況如下：<br />\n<br />\n1）開機去到Windows 10個logo 就停左，前面都冇事，試過等10個鐘都無反應，完全凍結咁<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/09/08/053606_329ec0c980a6a7e136d1ad1792440310.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F09%2F08%2F053606_329ec0c980a6a7e136d1ad1792440310.png&h=5d8065a4&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n2）Bios 係搵到E7600<br />\n<br />\n3）入唔到安全模式，重開幾次去到Logo 果到除左多左「準備自動修復」幾隻字又係咩都冇發生<br />\n<br />\n4）Keyboard mouse 係logo 個位停左陣就會自動熄晒<br />\n<br />\n5）全部零件拆晒插過晒 唔插USB 呢個方法都試過<br />\n<br />\n6）換番E2160又冇事<br />\n<br />\n7）試過用碟洗機都洗唔到 又係Logo位收左皮<br />\n<br />\n我估可能係CPU 有啲問題/底板bios 唔啱<br />\n但官網又話支援E7xxx系列 <br />\n而bios 又認到粒U<br />\ngoogle左兩日都係搞唔掂 <br />\n所以先勞煩咁多位巴打們打救下細佬<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-09-08T02:34:51.000Z","msg":"你部機係咪無UEFI?<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\nGoogle一下點樣入safe mode，入到之後reboot一次，應該就會入到Windows<br />\n再唔得就洗機，因為呢個係Windows問題，佢開機會辨識hardware，唔知點解換cpu/raid卡/底板都有機會出事，我見過好多次"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-08T06:22:50.000Z","msg":"直程係冇UEFI呢個options <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a5b7622b83748f8a73f56a49bb747286645a471e","tid":810262,"uid":120558,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"303de390bb5b1be7611fee5328ffc985ad99e1e1","tid":810262,"uid":33587,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-09-08T02:49:12.000Z","msg":"重裝咗windows未"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-0